The paper focuses on building and training complex, multi-modal models combining language and vision, which suggests that it belongs to the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL) and computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of neural networks and machine learning techniques, which are relevant to the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
